 *     BLUE / HALL_RL_A -> D0/WAKE            D1 <- HALL_RL_C / GREEN 
 *    GREEN / HALL_RR_C -> D5                 D2 <- HALL_RL_B / YELLOW
 *   YELLOW / HALL_RR_B -> D6            BOOT/D3
 *     BLUE / HALL_RR_A -> D7         LED/TX1/D4 -> ESF-MEAS @ 38400 -> ZED RXI
 *                         D8   FLASH        GND
